character_name: PerseusA fisherman who finds out he is a demigod
HadesGod of the underworld and the dead

IoA mortal woman who once refused the advances of a god and was cursed with agelessness. She has watched over Perseus and acts as his guide. The character is loosely inspired by the mythological figure of Io
King AcrisiusA mortal king who led a revolt against the gods. As punishment
